{"tid":2226420,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社民連悼「國殤」30警跟尾","createTime":"2020-10-02T04:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T04:51:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"71384eaf0daf6a5fe89cc79af74e84eb4758f28b","tid":2226420,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201002/UD5QKBOT2ZAOJNMMCMSFRYCT5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201002%2FUD5QKBOT2ZAOJNMMCMSFRYCT5U%2F&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=11736f42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201002%2FUD5QKBOT2ZAOJNMMCMSFRYCT5U%2F&h=36723713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201002/UD5QKBOT2ZAOJNMMCMSFRYCT5U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n社民連悼「國殤」30警跟尾<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社民連成員黃浩銘、梁國雄、古思堯及曾健成一行四人，昨早由灣仔港鐵站出發遊行至會展旁的萬麗海景酒店外，要求中共釋放包括12港人在內的所有政治犯，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：內媒：12港青或再押半年  律師質疑靠嚇 指案情非複雜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Lm9kW2rMpqk5Yp1dNkCPzwdhXSg=/1980x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C4IP4ZFFTZAQPPQ6IBKXB5J7ZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLm9kW2rMpqk5Yp1dNkCPzwdhXSg%3D%2F1980x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC4IP4ZFFTZAQPPQ6IBKXB5J7ZA.jpg&h=321e13f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■社民連四位成員遊行期間高呼叫口號，大批警員包圍式隨行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n燒請願信遭警告破壞秩序<br />\n<br />\n社民連成員遊行時高呼「沒有國慶，只有國殤」等口號，其間至少30名警員包圍式隨行，遊行路線上不時有警員駐守，各個天橋上亦有大量警員戒備。社民連一行人遊行至會展旁酒店時停步，並高呼「廢除國安惡法！釋放鹽田十二子！」<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄宣讀聲明後，嘗試將準備好的請願信燒毀，惟在場警員警告行為屬破壞公眾秩序，要求停止。貼上信件的公文袋被燒至斷開一半後，有警員上前以滅火器將之撲滅，地上留下一片白色粉末。<br />\n<br />\n另外，四名法輪功成員昨午拉起「天滅中共」等大字橫額，由西區警署遊行至中聯辦。他們到中聯辦門外以大聲公宣讀聲明，要求解體中共，批評國安法摧毁一國兩制，促請各國政府及民眾加大力度制止迫害。其間香港青年關愛協會到場，以大聲公指法輪功展示分裂國家的標語，違反港版國安法，要求當局嚴正執法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/X7hqwW_Tymg3uvx7x09VH4cFBaE=/1748x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O23DV6WFDZGOZNRJL5KINDYH6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FX7hqwW_Tymg3uvx7x09VH4cFBaE%3D%2F1748x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO23DV6WFDZGOZNRJL5KINDYH6Q.jpg&h=944c3619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曾健成（左）聲援被扣押內地的12名港青。"}]}